- Combine patterns and plugins into units that can be dropped in
    - All plugin patterns have equal priority (plugins loaded in alphabetical
      order) except for a specially designated 'default' plugin which always
      goes in last and typically contain the catch-all /.*/ pattern.
- Usage instructions
- Customization instructions
- An install script
    - Options:
      - Default install -- copy files into right locations
      - Dev install -- symlink files into location directly from git repo
